videos.description: Donta Hall gets Alabama going early against Oklahoma with a big two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Hall gets the Bama crowd going with a powerful slam

videos.description: Alabama's Collin Sexton takes advantage of a Sooners turnover and converts a layup in transition.
videos.headline: Sexton drives for fast-break bucket

videos.description: Avery Johnson Jr. makes a wild fast-break layup to keep the momentum in Alabama's favor.
videos.headline: Sexton hits Johnson Jr. for circus layup

videos.description: Alabama's Donta Hall gets it done on the defensive end with a big-time block.
videos.headline: Hall swats away layup attempt

videos.description: Collin Sexton finishes with authority on a fast break slam after Trae Young turns it over.
videos.headline: Sexton rises up with two hands on the fast break

videos.description: Trae Young blows past the Alabama defense then sends a no-look pass to Khadeem Lattin for the slam.
videos.headline: Young shows off handles to set up beautiful assist

videos.description: Herbert Jones gets his own rebound then makes a layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Jones hustles for layup plus the foul

videos.description: Collin Sexton speeds down the court for a transition layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Sexton explodes to rim for bucket

videos.description: Trae Young sinks a 3 from NBA range to keep the Sooners close.
videos.headline: Young responds with a deep 3

videos.description: Collin Sexton uses physicality to go baseline past Trae Young for layup.
videos.headline: Sexton gets physical with Young on drive to hoop

videos.description: Trae Young drills a stepback 3-pointer then silences the Alabama crowd.
videos.headline: Young shushes the crowd after stepback 3

videos.description: Alabama continues to push the tempo after Daniel Giddens hammers a dunk down through a foul.
videos.headline: Giddens rocks the rim in transition

videos.description: Trae Young gets caught in the air and turns it over, leading to a massive dunk by Herb Jones.
videos.headline: Jones abuses the rim on the fast break

videos.description: Alabama uses great ball movement to set up Braxton Key for an open 3-pointer to extend the Crimson Tide's scoring run.
videos.headline: Key's 3 caps Bama's 13-0 run

videos.description: Alabama slams down a dunk to push its lead  before Donta Hall comes up with another huge block to seal the game.
videos.headline: Alabama finishes Oklahoma at both ends of court

videos.description: Collin Sexton discusses his mentality entering the game against Oklahoma and what he needed to do to get the winning result.
videos.headline: Sexton says he proved he can win

videos.description: Avery Johnson loved how Alabama played for the name on the front of their uniforms, playing great team basketball.
videos.headline: Johnson says he saw his team mature in win

videos.description: Rich Hollenberg and Fran Fraschilla break down how Collin Sexton and Alabama were able to upset No. 12 Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Alabama uses full team performance to defeat OU 80-73

videos.description: In a matchup of two talented freshmen, Collin Sexton scores 18 points to Trae Young's 17 as the Crimson Tide come out on top.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Sexton, Bama get better of Young, Oklahoma) 2018/1/27 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Sexton, Bama get better of Young, Oklahoma

videos.description: Trae Young's 17 points are not enough as No. 12 Oklahoma loses to Collin Sexton and Alabama 80-73.
videos.headline: Alabama surges late to upend Oklahoma
